::Prowl/Striker::

An exciting feeling runs through Prowl as Iron Raptor puts her hand on his 
chest. He was already feeling quite detatched and light-headed due to all the 
emotion flowing through him.

He looks at Iron Raptor and then at Striker. He was a bit surprised that the 
two had already met, but decided not to ask about it. He looks at Striker's 
wounds, "Do you need any help?"

Striker nods at Iron Raptor's advice but shakes his head at Prowl's. "Nah, I 
can find my own way. I'll leave you two to your ... amusements...." He says, 
grinning and walking off.

Prowl blushes and turns back to Iron Raptor, his other hand and wing 
encircling her again. He looks at her face and grins. "I guess he caught us 
quite off-guard, didn't he?"
